headline: Brown Advisory Large-Cap Growth Strategy’s Updates on Fair Isaac Corporation (FICO)
summary: Brown Advisory, an investment management company, released its “Brown Advisory Large-Cap Growth Strategy” third-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here.
